WHAT A CATCH FROM HARMANPREET KAUR! Renuka Singh bowling to Aaliyah Alleyne, good length ball, pitching outside off stump, Aaliyah Alleyne tries to go down the ground, but Kaur at mid-on leaps to her right and plucks it one-handed - that's just extraordinary!
